title: AOL
description: AOL's brand colors embody a vibrant and diverse palette, featuring shades like black (000000), gray (808080), and several vivid tones including pink (FF00DE), green (4CFF00), blue (00CCFF), purple (6F00C2), red (FF0000), and orange (FF8600), all complemented by white for contrast (FFFFFF). These colors are referenced from their online sources, such as the AOL website and official digital platforms.
